name: EmbracingDigitalThisWeek
0:
”Alexa, play my Flash Briefing”
”Alexa, what's my Flash Briefing?”
skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
des: This skill lets users listen to the latest news from Embracing Digital Transformation's weekly podcast. It is supported on all Alexa audio devices. There are no pre-requests for this skill, which is used as a flash briefing.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
